            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Drain and rinse the <strong>black beans</strong></p><p>Once fragrant, add the <strong>drained black beans</strong>, a pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and 150ml<span class=\"text-danger\"> [250ml]</span><strong> cold water</strong> to the pan and bring to the boil</p><p>Reduce the heat to low and cook, covered, for 8-10 min or until the beans are beginning to soften</p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
